title=\"King-Beyond-the-Wall\">King-Beyond-the-Wall</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Andals,_the_Rhoynar,_and_the_First_Men\" title=\"King of the Andals, the Rhoynar, and the First Men\">King of the Andals, the Rhoynar, and the First Men</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Long_Night\" title=\"Long Night\">Long Night</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_the_Seven_Kingdoms\" title=\"Lord of the Seven Kingdoms\">Lord of the Seven Kingdoms</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Winterfell\" title=\"Lord of Winterfell\">Lord of Winterfell</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Master_of_horse\" title=\"Master of horse\">Master of horse</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Others\" title=\"Others\">Others</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Protector_of_the_Realm\" title=\"Protector of the Realm\">Protector of the Realm</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rhoynar\" title=\"Rhoynar\">Rhoynar</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Summerwine\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Summerwine\">Summerwine</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Valyrian_steel\" title=\"Valyrian steel\">Valyrian steel</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Warden_of_the_North\" title=\"Warden of the North\">Warden of the North</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Free_folk\" title=\"Free folk\">Wildling</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Wolf\" title=\"Wolf\">Wolf</a></li></ul>\n</div>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_links\">External links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_1&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: External links\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://blogofi